# Gauge.SU3

SU(3) gauge algebra.

The SU(3) gauge algebra is su(3) ≅ A₂ (rank-2 simple Lie algebra), spanned by
the 8 Gell-Mann matrices λ₁, …, λ₈ with generators Tₐ = λₐ/2.

In the Standard Model, SU(3)_c is the color gauge factor (QCD).
Quarks transform in the fundamental representation 3.
Gluons transform in the adjoint representation 8.

Status: stub.
